contentrichtext.text: [[File:Map of Russia - Altai Krai (2008-03).svg|thumb|right|Location of Altai Krai in Russia]] [[File:Map of Russia - Udmurt Republic (2008-03).svg|thumb|right|Location of Udmurt Republic in Russia]] '''Zavyalovsky District''' is the name of several administrative and municipal districts in [[Russia]]: *[[Zavyalovsky District, Altai Krai]], an administrative<ref name="AltaiK_adm">{{RussiaAdmMunRef|alt|adm|list}}</ref> and municipal<ref name="AltaiKZavyalovskyD_mun">{{RussiaAdmMunRef|alt|mun|list|zavyalovsky}}</ref> district of [[Altai Krai]] *[[Zavyalovsky District, Udmurt Republic]], an administrative<ref name="UdmurtR_adm">{{RussiaAdmMunRef|ud|adm|law}}</ref> and municipal<ref name="UdmurtRZavyalovskyD_mun">{{RussiaAdmMunRef|ud|mun|list|zavyalovsky}}</ref> district of the [[Udmurt Republic]] ==References== {{Reflist}} {{SIA|Russian districts}}
